issue.title: [CF 1544] GetChannelList() return values have changed
issue.body:
Since one of the hotfix patches, there are now 3 parameters returned from GetChannelList().  It's wrecking havoc with various add-ons, and I noticed TellMeWhen had some calls.


> Posted by CurseForge user Caerdon | Imported from CurseForge issue #1544 | Raw
